	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64589185"><p><nobr> <wbr></nobr></p><div class="quote"><p>...but there's no atmosphere to let that heat radiate away.</p></div><p>
You do not need an atmosphere to radiate the heat away - in fact radiating heat away is the only to lose heat in a vacuum. What you mean is convect the heat away which is much better at removing heat than radiating it.</p></div>
